# 🚀 End-to-End ML Model Deployment (FastAPI + Docker)

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates a complete **Machine Learning deployment pipeline** — from model training to production deployment using FastAPI and Docker.

The API predicts outcomes based on input features and is designed to be scalable, containerized, and cloud-ready.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Train and evaluate a machine learning model
* Build a REST API using FastAPI
* Containerize the application using Docker
* Deploy the API to cloud platforms
* Monitor performance and maintain model lifecycle

